Soak @chickpeas{200%g} in water for a few hours.

Dice @white onion{1} and set until translucent in a #pressure cooker{}. 
Add @garlic gloves{3} and @ginger{2%tsp} (grated). 
Sate and add spices: @garam masala{}, @turmeric, @cumin, @coriander, @chilli powder{}, @Kashmiri chilli powder{}.

Add @tomatoes{2%can} and the soaked chickpeas. Cook for ~{20%min} in the pressure cooker. 

Serve with rice, parathas or roti.